{
  "name": "SparkColor",
  "summary": "<p><strong>SparkColor</strong> 对象对应于功能区 <strong>“迷你图工具设计”</strong> 选项卡的 <strong>“样式”</strong> 部分中 <strong>“标记颜色”</strong> 下拉列表中提供的项的设置。使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkPoints/SparkPoints .htm#SparkPoints.SparkPoints\">SparkPoints</a></strong> 对象的对应属性可设置这些项的颜色。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 A1:A4 中第一个迷你图组的迷你图的最高数据点设置为可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparkColor = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Points</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Highpoint</span>\n    sparkColor.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 A1:A4 中第一个迷你图组的迷你图的最后一个数据点设置为可见，并设置其颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparkColor = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Points</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Lastpoint</span>\n    sparkColor.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    sparkColor.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示迷你图中的点的标记色。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Color",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong> 对象，可使用该对象来设置迷你图中点的标记色。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A4 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparkColor = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axis</span>\n    sparkColor.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上区域 A1:A4 中第一个迷你图组的迷你图的第一个数据点可见，则将该数据点设置为黑色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparkColor = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Points</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Firstpoint</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (sparkColor.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span>) {\n        sparkColor.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong>FormatColor</strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Visible",
      "summary": "<p><strong>Visible</strong> 属性的设置对应于功能区 <strong>“迷你图工具设计”</strong> 选项卡 <strong>“显示”</strong> 部分中的 <strong>“高点”</strong>、<strong>“低点”</strong>、<strong>“负点”</strong>、<strong>“首点”</strong>、<strong>“尾点”</strong> 和 <strong>­“标记”</strong> 复选框的设置。使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkPoints/SparkPoints .htm#SparkPoints.SparkPoints\">SparkPoints</a></strong> 对象的对应属性可设置这些复选框的状态。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置点是否可见。可读/写</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将区域 A1:A4 上第一个迷你图组的迷你图的正数据点设置为不可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparkColor = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Points</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Markers</span>\n    sparkColor.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示���显示区域 A1:A4 上第一个迷你图组的迷你图的负数据点是否可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparkColor = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Points</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Negative</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparkColor.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}